In Virtue is a US based guild on a european server (Kane Bayle). To put it straight, this server has no population or competition and we all spawns to ourselves. Because of this low population we have no pool from which to recruit, that is why we are xserver recruiting. Our player base is already Elemental Flagged, and even if you are not, we will begin the reflagging process in upcoming weeks for those who need them.<br>
<br>
Raid Times &amp; Attendance-<br>
We are a US based guild and raid daily starting at 7pm EST. All members are expected to be on for at least 5 day a week during raid time. If we have a planned raid that involves getting a flag, you must attend the raid or make arrangements to have someone &quot;bot&quot; you so you can get the flag. <br>
<br>
Requirements-<br>
The following requirements must be met if you are planning on applying to In Virtue. All applicants must be Level 65.<br>
If you are a cross server applicant, you must have PoV/PoS, BoT, HoHA flags. If you are flagged upto the elemental planes already, that is a huge bonus. <br>
